727367f-a.title: Queens: Maspeth Avenue - 60th Street
727367f-a.text:
Maspeth Ave., north side, in 60th Street, showing the Kolyer
farmhouse which was demolished in April 1923. This house stood
directly on what is 60th Street today. P.S. No. 12 is directly
opposite the site. In the background are homes on the north side
of 56th Drive.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
